OL,3,CPolice at scene of two sudden deaths
OL,4,Cin Co Tyrone
OL,6,FPolice are at the scene of two sudden
OL,7,Fdeaths in Co Tyrone.
OL,9,FA PSNI spokesperson said on Tuesday
OL,10,Fnight that the Garvaghy Road in Omagh
OL,11,Fwas closed and the public was asked to
OL,12,Favoid the area.
OL,14,FThe spokesperson said an update would
OL,15,Fbe provided later.
